---
---

<section id="features" class="features">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="section-tag">Engine</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Technical Architecture</h2>
      <p class="section-desc">Packet-level DPI evasion. No tunnels, no proxies. WinDivert intercepts and modifies TCP streams in kernel space.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="features-grid">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon-wrap">
          <svg class="feature-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"/>
            <path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5"/>
            <path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>WinDivert Packet Interception</h3>
        <p>WinDivert v2.2 kernel driver captures, filters, and modifies raw TCP/UDP packets at the network layer (L3). Winws2 engine performs TCP desynchronization and packet reordering — the core mechanism that breaks DPI signature matching.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon-wrap">
          <svg class="feature-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <polygon points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Zero Throughput Overhead</h3>
        <p>Only packets destined for blocked domains are modified. All other traffic — banking, government, CDN — passes through unaltered. No encapsulation, no remote hops, no MTU penalty. Full native bandwidth is preserved.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon-wrap">
          <svg class="feature-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/>
            <path d="M19.4 15a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 .33 1.82l.06.06a2 2 0 1 1-2.83 2.83l-.06-.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.82-.33 1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1 1.51V21a2 2 0 0 1-4 0v-.09A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 9 19.4a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.82.33l-.06.06a2 2 0 1 1-2.83-2.83l.06-.06A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 4.68 15a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.51-1H3a2 2 0 0 1 0-4h.09A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 4.6 9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-.33-1.82l-.06-.06a2 2 0 1 1 2.83-2.83l.06.06A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 9 4.68a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1-1.51V3a2 2 0 0 1 4 0v.09a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1 1.51 1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.82-.33l.06-.06a2 2 0 1 1 2.83 2.83l-.06.06A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 19.4 9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.51 1H21a2 2 0 0 1 0 4h-.09a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.51 1z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Parallel Profile Probing</h3>
        <p>Auto-detection concurrently test-fires profiles against canonical endpoints (YouTube, Discord, Instagram, Twitter, RuTracker). The selection algorithm picks the minimal-modification profile that resolves all targets — no brute force, no guesswork.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon-wrap">
          <svg class="feature-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"/>
            <path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>GPL-3.0 — Fully Auditable</h3>
        <p>Every dependency ships inline: Lua DPI-evasion scripts, WinDivert driver binaries, winws2 engine — compiled into a single executable. No hidden fetch calls, no telemetry, no external dependencies. Source is the artifact.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon-wrap">
          <svg class="feature-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0z"/>
            <line x1="12" y1="9" x2="12" y2="13"/>
            <line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Conflict Detection</h3>
        <p>Enumerates running services and flags incompatibilities with GoodbyeDPI, Zapret, OpenVPN, Cloudflare WARP, and commercial VPN clients. WinDivert operates at L3 — concurrent packet-level filters cause undefined behavior and are blocked preemptively.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon-wrap">
          <svg class="feature-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <polyline points="4 17 10 11 4 5"/>
            <line x1="12" y1="19" x2="20" y2="19"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Silent Scheduled Launch</h3>
        <p>Registers a Windows Task Scheduler entry for UAC-bypassed startup into the system tray. No console window, no elevation prompt on boot. Runs as a background process with the same kernel-level privileges required at install time.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.features {
  padding: 8rem 2rem;
  position: relative;
}

.container {
  max-width: 1152px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.section-header {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 4rem;
}

.section-tag {
  display: inline-block;
  padding: 4px 12px;
  border-radius: 100px;
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  font-weight: 500;
  font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 1.5px;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
}

.section-title {
  font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 2.5rem);
  font-weight: 700;
  font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
  margin: 0 0 8px;
  letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
}

.section-desc {
  font-size: 0.9375rem;
  line-height: 1.6;
  max-width: 560px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45);
  font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
}

.features-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 16px;
}

.feature-card {
  padding: 24px;
  border-radius: 12px;
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
  transition: background 0.2s ease, border-color 0.2s ease;
}

.feature-card:hover {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
  border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
}

.feature-icon-wrap {
  width: 32px;
  height: 32px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  border-radius: 8px;
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
}

.feature-icon {
  width: 16px;
  height: 16px;
}

.feature-card h3 {
  font-size: 0.875rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
  margin: 0 0 8px;
  letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
}

.feature-card p {
  line-height: 1.6;
  font-size: 0.8125rem;
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
  font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
  margin: 0;
}

@media (max-width: 1024px) {
  .features-grid {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
  }
}

@media (max-width: 640px) {
  .features-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }
  .features {
    padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
  }
  .section-header {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
}
</style>
